1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,522
Danger is not rage.

2
00:00:01,522 --> 00:00:03,204
Rage removes options.

3
00:00:03,204 --> 00:00:06,248
Real capability is
staying calm enough

4
00:00:06,248 --> 00:00:09,132
to see three
constructive moves when

5
00:00:09,132 --> 00:00:10,974
everyone else sees one.

6
00:00:10,974 --> 00:00:13,618
Start with ten
phone-free minutes

7
00:00:13,618 --> 00:00:14,098
today.

8
00:00:14,098 --> 00:00:17,062
When the urge to escape
appears, name

9
00:00:17,062 --> 00:00:17,302
it.

10
00:00:17,302 --> 00:00:18,504
Do not obey it.

11
00:00:18,504 --> 00:00:21,548
That gap between
impulse and action is

12
00:00:21,548 --> 00:00:23,230
where command begins.
